      "value": "<p>Beginning at 14th level, you gain the ability to counterattack when your target tries to sabotage you. </p><p>If your Primary Target forces you to make a saving throw, you can use your reaction to make one weapon attack against them. </p><p>You make this attack immediately before making the saving throw. </p><p>If the attack hits, you gain advantage on the saving throw.</p>",
